{{!< default}}

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-center">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">A Nozomi Content Series</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">The Last Decade of <span class="accent-word">Freedom</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Fundraising and growth resources to help Web3 founders beat their Web2 competition. Because the builders who win the next decade decide what comes after.</p>

        <form class="hero-form" data-members-form="signup">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required />
            <button type="submit">Get Access</button>
        </form>
        <p class="hero-fineprint">Free. No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
        <div class="hero-ornament">望</div>
    </div>
</section>

{{!-- Latest Letters --}}
<section class="letters-section">
  <div class="topics-row">
    <span class="topics-label">Topics</span>
    <button class="topic-chip is-active" data-filter="all">All</button>
    <button class="topic-chip" data-filter="the-case-for-web3">The Case for Web3</button>
    <button class="topic-chip" data-filter="web3-growth-marketing">Web3 Growth &amp; Marketing</button>
    <button class="topic-chip" data-filter="web3-startup-ideas">Web3 Startup Ideas</button>
    <button class="topic-chip" data-filter="fundraising">Fundraising</button>
    <button class="topic-chip" data-filter="self-sovereign-ideas">Self-Sovereign Ideas</button>
    <button class="topic-chip" data-filter="project-deep-dives">Project Deep Dives</button>
  </div>

  <div class="letters-list">
    {{#if posts}}
      {{#foreach posts}}
        <article class="letter-card" data-tags="{{#foreach tags}}{{slug}} {{/foreach}}">
          {{#if feature_image}}
            <a class="letter-card-image" href="{{url}}">
              <img src="{{img_url feature_image size="l"}}" alt="{{title}}" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
          {{/if}}
          <div class="letter-card-body">
            {{#if primary_tag}}<div class="letter-card-meta-top">{{primary_tag.name}}</div>{{/if}}
            <h3 class="letter-card-title"><a href="{{url}}">{{title}}</a></h3>
            {{#if excerpt}}<p class="letter-card-excerpt">{{excerpt words="28"}}</p>{{/if}}
            <div class="letter-card-meta-bottom">
              {{#if primary_author}}{{primary_author.name}} · {{/if}}{{reading_time}} · {{date published_at format="MMM DD, YYYY"}}
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      {{/foreach}}
    {{else}}
      <div class="letters-empty">First letter coming soon.</div>
    {{/if}}
  </div>
</section>

{{!-- What You Get --}}
<section class="get-section">
    <div class="get-header">
        <div class="section-label">What You Get</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Every week in your inbox</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="get-grid">
        <div class="get-card">
            <div class="get-card-icon">📖</div>
            <h3>Deep-Dive Articles</h3>
            <p>Long-form explorations of the real problems crypto solves. No jargon, no shilling. Accessible to anyone, even if they've never bought a token.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="get-card">
            <div class="get-card-icon">🚀</div>
            <h3>Startup Ideas</h3>
            <p>Every article includes a concrete "Request for Startups". What's not yet being built, and what Nozomi would incubate and support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="get-card">
            <div class="get-card-icon">🗺</div>
            <h3>Fundraising &amp; Growth Playbooks</h3>
            <p>Step-by-step implementation guides to help founders plan, raise, and launch. From idea to TGE and beyond, with frameworks you can action immediately.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{{!-- Why this series exists --}}
<section class="prose-section">
    <div class="prose-block">
        <div class="section-label">Why this series exists</div>
        <p>The next decade decides humanity's future. AI, robotics, and brain-computer interfaces are accelerating at a pace most people do not fully grasp. Whoever controls the models controls the future. First they control your wealth. Then what you see. Then what you think. We are walking into a world where Orwell's 1984 is not fiction. It is the default trajectory.</p>
        <p>The one technology built to fight back is still dismissed as a scam. But underneath the noise, decentralisation is the most important technological movement of our lifetime. It is the only path to a world where humans are at the center and technology serves them, instead of the other way around.</p>
        <p>This newsletter exists to help the builders win. Fundraising and growth playbooks for the founders beating their Web2 competition. No hype. No token shilling. Just the real work that moves the needle, and the ideas that push the space forward.</p>
    </div>
</section>

{{!-- Final CTA --}}
<section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-inner">
        <div class="hero-ornament cta-ornament">望</div>
        <h2 class="cta-title">The next decade decides everything.</h2>
        <p class="cta-desc">Decentralisation is how we fight back. This series is the ammunition. Get it free, every week.</p>
        <form class="hero-form cta-form" data-members-form="signup">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required />
            <button type="submit">Get Access</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>
